PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773691869
OL,3,CMan jailed for 23 years after fatal
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for 23 years
OL,7,Fafter he fatally stabbed a man
OL,8,Fmultiple times.
OL,10,FMartin Alan Davies, 36, killed Kailem
OL,11,FGibson in Newton Heath on 29 August
OL,12,F2025 after attacking him with a knife
OL,13,Fat an address before fleeing.
OL,15,FKailem, 20, was taken to hospital with
OL,16,Flife threatening injuries where, the
OL,17,Fcourt heard, he died the next day.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
