OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773691869
OL,3,CMan jailed for 23 years after fatal
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,FIn a statement Kailem's family said he
OL,7,F"was full of life and had a
OL,8,Fpersonality that could light up any
OL,9,Froom".
OL,11,F"He was funny, always laughing and
OL,12,Fjoking and he had a way of making the
OL,13,Fmost out of everything," they added.
OL,15,F"He never took life too seriously and
OL,16,Falways managed to make people smile
OL,17,Feven in difficult moments.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773691869
OL,3,CMan jailed for 23 years after fatal
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,F"To us Kailem was so much more than
OL,7,Fthe victim of a crime. He was a loving
OL,8,Fson, brother, father, nephew, cousin
OL,9,Fand friend, and he meant the world to
OL,10,Four family.
OL,12,F"His laughter, energy and kindness
OL,13,Ftouched everyone who knew him and his
OL,14,Fabsence has left a hole in our lives
OL,15,Fthat can never be filled."
OL,17,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP)
OL,18,Fofficers detained Davies on Oakley
OL,19,FClose and arrested him on suspicion of
OL,20,Fa serious assault shortly after the
OL,21,Fincident.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773691869
OL,3,CMan jailed for 23 years after fatal
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,FHe was later further arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder, and an
OL,8,Finvestigation was launched.
OL,10,FA jury found Davies not guilty of
OL,11,Fmurder and guilty of manslaughter
OL,12,Ffollowing a two week trial at
OL,13,FManchester Crown Court in February
OL,14,F2026.
OL,16,FHe was sentenced to 19 years in
OL,17,Fprison, with another four years added
OL,18,Fon his licence period on 16 March 2026.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773691869
OL,3,CMan jailed for 23 years after fatal
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,FKailem's family's statement continued:
OL,7,F"It wasn't the outcome we wanted and
OL,8,Fit does not take the pain our family
OL,9,Ffeels every single day. Nothing can
OL,10,Fbring Kailem back and the loss we
OL,11,Fcarry will remain with us forever.
OL,13,F"We would like to thank the police and
OL,14,Flegal team who worked hard to bring
OL,15,Fthe case to court, as well as everyone
OL,16,Fwho has supported our family during
OL,17,Fthis incredibly difficult time.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773691869
OL,3,CMan jailed for 23 years after fatal
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,F"We also want to use this moment to
OL,7,Fsay clearly that knife crime is
OL,8,Ftotally unacceptable and no family
OL,9,Fshould have to experience the pain and
OL,10,Fdevastation that comes from using a
OL,11,Fknife and losing a loved one in this
OL,12,Fway.
OL,14,F"Our hope is that Kailem's story
OL,15,Freminds people of the devastating
OL,16,Fconsequences of violence and
OL,17,Fencourages change so that other
OL,18,Ffamilies do not have to go through
OL,19,Fwhat we have.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773691869
OL,3,CMan jailed for 23 years after fatal
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,F"We will continue to remember Kailem
OL,7,Ffor the joy he brought into our lives.
OL,8,FKailem was and is still deeply loved
OL,9,Fand will always be remembered. His
OL,10,Fmemory will live on in our hearts
OL,11,Fforever.
OL,13,F"We kindly ask that our family's
OL,14,Fprivacy is respected as we continue to
OL,15,Fgrieve."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773691869
OL,3,CMan jailed for 23 years after fatal
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Louise
OL,7,FEdwards, from GMP's Major Incident
OL,8,FTeam, said: "I hope Kailem's family
OL,9,Fand loved ones feel a sense of justice
OL,10,Ffollowing today's sentencing, and that
OL,11,Fthey can now be left to grieve Kailem
OL,12,Fin peace and privacy.
OL,14,F"This was a shocking incident where a
OL,15,Fyoung man's life was taken. Our
OL,16,Fthoughts will always remain with
OL,17,FKailem, his family and his loved ones.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773691869
OL,3,CMan jailed for 23 years after fatal
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,F"I would like to thank the
OL,7,Finvestigation team for their hard work
OL,8,Fduring the investigation and trial. I
OL,9,Falso want to thank Kailem's family for
OL,10,Ftheir support throughout the
OL,11,Finvestigation."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
